trans-unit.source: Represents a single [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element in an [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] project.
trans-unit.target: Representerer én [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element i en [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] prosjektet.

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified [Task](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element to the [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element.
trans-unit.target: Legger til den angitte [oppgaven](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) elementet som den [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) elementet.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask"></xref> object that represents the <xref uid="langword_csharp_Task" name="Task" href=""></xref> element to add to the <xref uid="langword_csharp_Target" name="Target" href=""></xref> element.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask"> </xref> objektet som representerer den <xref uid="langword_csharp_Task" name="Task" href=""> </xref> elementet til å legge til den <xref uid="langword_csharp_Target" name="Target" href=""> </xref> elementet.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask"></xref> object represents a child `Task` element of the `Target` element.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask"> </xref> objektet representerer en underordnet `Task` element av den `Target` elementet.

trans-unit.source: Gets the `Condition` attribute value of the [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element.
trans-unit.target: Henter den `Condition` attributt verdien for den [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) elementet.

trans-unit.source: The `Condition` attribute value of the `Target` element.
trans-unit.target: Den `Condition` attributt verdien for den `Target` elementet.

trans-unit.source: Gets the `DependsOnTargets` attribute value of the [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element, which is a semicolon-separated list.
trans-unit.target: Henter den `DependsOnTargets` attributt verdien for den [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element, som er en liste med atskilt med semikolon.

trans-unit.source: The `DependsOnTargets` attribute value of the `Target` element.
trans-unit.target: Den `DependsOnTargets` attributt verdien for den `Target` elementet.

trans-unit.source: Gets an enumerator that iterates through the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask"></xref> objects in the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter en opplisting som går gjennom den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask"> </xref> objekter i den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This method allows the caller to use the `foreach` statement of the C# language (`for each` in [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)]) to iterate through the individual <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask> objects in the <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target>.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kan oppkalleren å bruke den `foreach` -setningen for språket C# (`for each` i [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)]) å gå gjennom de individuelle <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask>objekter i <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target>.</xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target> </xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask> object represents a child element of the `Target` element.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask>objektet som representerer et underordnet element av den `Target` element.</xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator> for the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask"></xref> objects in the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>for den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask"> </xref> objekter i den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"> </xref>.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the items that are to be input into this target.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir elementene som skal være inndata til dette målet.

trans-unit.source: Items inside this target attribute are used as the inputs in the top level dependency analysis.
trans-unit.target: Elementene i denne Målattributtet brukes som inndata i analysen øverste nivå avhengighet.

trans-unit.source: A string representing the items.
trans-unit.target: En streng som representerer elementene.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element was imported into the project.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om den [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) elementet ble importert i prosjektet.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the `Target` element was imported into the project; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis den `Target` ble importert til prosjektet; ellers, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the `Name` attribute value of the [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element.
trans-unit.target: Henter den `Name` attributt verdien for den [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) elementet.

trans-unit.source: The `Name` attribute value of the `Target` element.
trans-unit.target: Den `Name` attributt verdien for den `Target` elementet.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the expected outputs of this target.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir de forventede utdataene for dette målet.

trans-unit.source: You can apply transforms to this target attribute to transform a set of input items into a set of output items.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke transformeringer på dette attributtet target transformere et sett med inndata elementer i et sett med output-elementer.

trans-unit.source: This attribute is used not only for top level dependency analysis but also for the purposes of defining this targets outputs.
trans-unit.target: Dette attributtet brukes ikke bare for øverste nivå avhengighet analyse, men også for å definere denne mål-utdataene.

trans-unit.source: A string representing the outputs.
trans-unit.target: En streng som representerer utdataene.

trans-unit.source: Removes the specified [Task](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element from the [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element.
trans-unit.target: Fjerner det angitte [oppgaven](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) elementet fra den [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) elementet.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask> object represents a child `Task` element of the `Target` element.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask>objektet representerer en underordnet `Task` element av den `Target` element.</xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask"></xref> object that represents the <xref uid="langword_csharp_Task" name="Task" href=""></xref> element to remove from the <xref uid="langword_csharp_Target" name="Target" href=""></xref> element.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask"> </xref> objektet som representerer den <xref uid="langword_csharp_Task" name="Task" href=""> </xref> elementet til å fjerne fra den <xref uid="langword_csharp_Target" name="Target" href=""> </xref> elementet.
